your_project/
│
├── app.py               # Your main Flask app script
├── .env                 # Environment variables (SECRET_KEY, MONGO_URI, etc.)
├── requirements.txt     # Python dependencies (Flask, pymongo, Flask-Login, etc.)
├── templates/           # Folder containing all HTML templates
│   ├── login.html
│   ├── registration.html
│   ├── main.html
│   ├── team.html
│   └── profile.html
├── static/              # Folder for static files like CSS, JS, images
│   └── css/
│       └── style.css    # Your main CSS file
└── README.md            # Optional, project documentation

